===Smart Contract Invocation for NEP-5 token transfer URI===
To invoke the smart contract, we need to specify a script hash and the operation of the smart contract that is being invoked as well as providing required parameters. This way an application can tailor the screen to match the invoking operation with pre-filled information. e.g. transfer NEP-5 token, voting, etc. what left for a user to do is to authorize/sign the transaction. It would have the following URI. 

<code>neo:<ScriptHash>?operation=<operation>[&<parameterName>=<parameterValue>][&<TransactionAttributeKey>=<value>]</code>

